```plantuml
@startuml domingo1021_Bunny-code

actor User
participant "Web Browser" as Browser
participant "Nginx Reverse Proxy" as Nginx
participant "Node.js Backend" as Backend
participant "MySQL Database" as MySQL
participant "InfluxDB" as InfluxDB
participant "Redis Cache" as Redis
participant "Docker Sandbox" as Sandbox
participant "S3 Storage" as S3
participant "CloudFront CDN" as CloudFront
participant "CloudWatch Monitoring" as CloudWatch

User -> Browser : Access Bunny Code Platform
Browser -> Nginx : Request API/Data
Nginx -> Backend : Forward Request
Backend -> MySQL : Query User/Project Data
MySQL --> Backend : Return Data
Backend -> InfluxDB : Query Time-series Data
InfluxDB --> Backend : Return Data
Backend -> Redis : Check Cache/State
Redis --> Backend : Return Cached Data
Backend -> Sandbox : Execute User Code
Sandbox --> Backend : Return Execution Result
Backend -> S3 : Store/Retrieve Files
S3 --> Backend : Return File URL
Backend -> CloudWatch : Send Logs/Monitoring Data
Backend -> Nginx : Response
Nginx -> Browser : Deliver Content via CloudFront
Browser -> User : Display Response

@enduml
```